These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: brazilian, pakistani, polish, argentine
1. Nationality:pakistani is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:argentine is between Nationality:brazilian and Nationality:pakistani##2
3. Nationality:argentine is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | argentine | pakistani | polish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: pepper, tomato, lime, radish
1. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:radish##1
2. Food:tomato is in an odd position##4
3. Food:tomato is on the left or right of Food:pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | tomato | pepper | radish | lime |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: musical, comedy, fantasy, western
1. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:musical##3
2. Movie-Genre:musical is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:fantasy is between Movie-Genre:western and Movie-Genre:comedy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | western | fantasy | comedy |

 #################################
 
