.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: apricot, orange, pear, pepper
1. Food:orange == Food:orange##1
2. Food:pepper is on the left or right of Food:pear##3
3. Food:pear is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:apricot is in an even position##4
5. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | pear | pepper | orange | apricot |

